ygData.msgSnippet: try connecting at a lower speed. else try going under the dialer properties, under the modem configuration, go to Connection - Advanced and in the extra
ygData.messageBody:
try connecting at a lower speed.

else try going under the dialer properties, under the modem configuration,
go to Connection -> Advanced and in the extra settings put in either ATZ or
at&f1
